HEADWORD: Improving
<hw>Im*prov"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Tending to
improve, beneficial; growing better.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Im*prov"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Improving lease</b></col> <fld>(Scots Law)</fld>, <cd>an
extended lease to induce the tenant to make improvements on the
premises.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Improvisate</ent>⟦br⟧
